---
const technologies = [
  {
    name: "React",
    icon: "https://reactjs.org/favicon.ico",
  },
  {
    name: "TypeScript",
    icon: "https://www.typescriptlang.org/favicon.ico",
  },
  {
    name: "Next.js",
    icon: "https://nextjs.org/favicon.ico",
  },
  {
    name: "Tailwind CSS",
    icon: "https://tailwindcss.com/favicon.ico",
  },
];
---

<section id="tecnologias" class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-muted/30">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-4xl">
        Stack Tecnológico
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-muted-foreground">
        Trabalhamos com as tecnologias mais modernas do ecossistema React.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          React
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          Next.js
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          TypeScript
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          Tailwind CSS
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          Redux
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          Zustand
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          React Query
        </div>
        <!-- <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          GraphQL
        </div> -->
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          Jest
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          Testing Library
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          Playwright
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          Vitest
        </div>
        <!-- <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          Webpack
        </div> -->
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          Vite
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          Turbopack
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground"
        >
          ESLint
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
            Especialização em React
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">
            Nossa equipe é formada por desenvolvedores certificados e
            especializados em React, com experiência comprovada em projetos de
            grande escala para empresas nacionais e internacionais.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">
            Mantemos-nos sempre atualizados com as últimas tendências e melhores
            práticas do ecossistema React, garantindo que seu projeto utilize as
            tecnologias mais adequadas e modernas.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <div
            class="flex h-64 w-64 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-border bg-card"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="120"
              height="120"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="text-primary"
            >
              <path d="m18 16 4-4-4-4"></path>
              <path d="m6 8-4 4 4 4"></path>
              <path d="m14.5 4-5 16"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
